---
title: Double Crumbed Fish & Chips with Garden Salad & Tartare Sauce
description: It’s a classic, it’s a favourite for all, it’s the answer to your cravings, a steaming plate of fish and chips. That’s right we’re trying
our hand at this superstar dish, bringing it to your kitchen with a garlic and herb crumb for the dory fish fillets, a must-have
side of chips, fresh salad and of course a tartare sauce. You won’t be needing that takeaway menu anymore.
